Reconstruction for 2CVs in a 3D space and view in GNUPLOT as
static graph and as GIF animation through ImageMagick (for e.g. animate)

Vreco_CPMD.f90 input file: vreco.inp
Vreco_CPMD.f90 output    : vreco.out
shell script for GNUPLOT : view_gnuplot_script 
                           - plot V.final.out to postscript file fes-example-1.ps
                           - plot V.dynamic.out and convert to fes-dyn-example-1.gif

